title: Guns N' Roses: Use Your Illusion 1 World Tour  - 1992 [Tokyo]
description:
Use Your Illusion I is a live VHS/DVD by Guns N' Roses. Filmed live at the Tokyo Dome, Japan in 1992 on the Use Your Illusion tour, this recording features the first half of the concert, the second half appearing on the sister volume, Use Your Illusion II. The VHS titles were distributed by Geffen Home Video in 1992.

The songs "Pretty Tied Up", "Don't Cry" and "November Rain" from this event were used in the band's 1999 live album Live Era: '87-'93.

Full DVD rip ISO image.
In NTSC format, with 5.1 Dolby Digital.
